parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the rear liftgate panel can lead to water entry, compromising the internal components and potentially causing electrical shorts, which can increase the risk of accidents. Additionally, the cracked panel can compromise the security of the vehicle, allowing unauthorized access.
symptoms: A vertical crack appears on the rear liftgate panel
often near the Lincoln emblem
which can lead to water entry and damage to internal components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shift can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park or another gear, making it difficult or impossible to operate the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shift becomes stuck in park or another gear
the gear shift detaches from the vehicle
the vehicle is unable to shift out of park
the gear shift is difficult to move
the vehicle rolls away in reverse.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle can cause the vehicle to lose control, making it difficult to steer or brake, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear axle starts to come out of the vehicle while moving
the vehicle develops a "death wobble" and appears to be driving erratically
the rear wheel bearings fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shift can cause the vehicle to slip or hesitate, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the O/D sensor light comes on
the vehicle makes a whining or siren sound in the rear end.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended deployment of airbags can cause physical harm, distraction, and loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Airbag deploys without any impact or crash
airbag deploys while starting the vehicle
airbag deploys on the wrong side (e.g.
passenger side instead of driver side)
seat belt warnings appear despite all occupants being properly restrained.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to ineffective protection in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injuries and fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag fails to deploy on the correct side
airbag fails to deploy at all
seat belt warnings appear despite all occupants being properly restrained
uncertainty about the airbag system's functionality.
